### expected behaviour
user should have full permissions in a folder shared with him. this was so in owncloud 4.5.x

### actual behaviour
if i share a folder read-only with group, and share then a subfolder with a member of this group with full permissions this member of the group does not have full permissions in this folder.

### steps to reproduce

1. make a folder
2. share it read-only with a group
3. share a subfolder from the folder in [1] with a specific user from the group in [2] with full rights
4. the specified user from [3] cannot write, move, delete or re-share in the shared subfolder




### server configuration
operating system: debian 6 and debian 7

web server: apache 2

database: sqlite and mysql

php version: 5.3.3-7+squeeze15 and 5.4.4-14

owncloud version: 5.0.6 and 5.0.7rc1

### client configuration
browser: chrome/firefox/ie

operating system: windows 7

